  Accounts
  Choose an account, auth flow, or fork setting.
  This session: none
  Shared active account: API key (...1234)

› 1. Login with ChatGPT               Start browser login and wait for the callback.
  2. Login with device code           Show a one-time code for browser sign-in.
  3. Add API key                      Enter an API key and make it the active account.
  4. Switch account                   1 saved account(s) available.
  5. Switch to shared active account  Another Codex instance activated API key (...1234). Adopt it
                                      in this session.
  6. Remove account                   Delete a saved auth blob from ~/.codex/.accounts/.
  7. View account limits              View the latest saved-account usage and reset times.
  8. Settings                         Change account settings.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
